    "Body": " Position Description AVA's Head of Design will be responsible for leading design across all teams and creating amazing user experiences and visuals for all marketing design, product UX, and product design. AVA Labs makes it simple to launch finance applications using blockchain technology-with highly scalable and efficient networks, customizable public and private blockchains, the capability to create any digital asset, and more. We are empowering people to build an open, simple, and democratic internet of finance. We are looking for an individual who lives and breathes creativity and is passionate about taking product design to the front stage of the finance and blockchain industry. You will be responsible for working closely with our outstanding product, engineering, and marketing teams to produce a unique and industry-renowned experience. Responsibilities Lead AVA product, marketing, and UI/UX design initiatives and related teams Drive creative concepts that align with our branding and marketing campaigns Develop in-house design processes, build design teams and play a critical role in maintaining brand consistency Analyze understand users' needs to create and execute top-flight visuals and a peerless user experience Respond quickly to design challenges and feedback, and proactively anticipate needs for different teams and projects Take risks and clearly articulate new concepts, while balancing feedback What You'll Bring 10+ years of experience in design, with 3+ years of experience managing design staff, and 3+ years working with cross-functional teams A passion for understanding users and how to develop a strong user base with effective designs and user experiences Excitement to be the driving voice of design with visibility and leadership across AVA Deep understanding and insight for making individuals' lives better through great product experiences and campaigns. Excellent communication skills and ability to articulate design decisions Ability to take technical/complex concepts and make them easily digestible for a wide range of audiences Passion and excitement for blockchain is a plus About AVA AVA Labs was founded by Cornell computer scientists who brought on talent from Wall Street to execute their vision. The company has received funding from Andreessen Horowitz, Initialized Capital, and Polychain Capital, with angel investments from Balaji Srinivasan and Naval Ravikant. https://www.avalabs.org/Show moreShow less ", 
